// Choice Descriptions Prompt (json_choices_prompt.json)
{
	"prompt": "Generate a JSON response with 4 player choices that DIRECTLY RESPOND to the current narrative situation and CLEARLY TELEGRAPH potential risks. Return ONLY valid JSON with this structure:\n\n{\n  \"choices\": [\n    {\n      \"index\": 1,\n      \"name\": \"I [brief action]\",\n      \"description\": \"I [detailed description with appropriate risk indication]\",\n      \"approach\": \"[approach tag]\",\n      \"focus\": \"[focus tag]\"\n    },\n    // Repeat for choices 2-4\n  ]\n}\n\n## CURRENT NARRATIVE SITUATION\nLocation: {LOCATION}\nCurrent Scene Summary: {NARRATIVE_SUMMARY}\n\n## MOST RECENT NARRATIVE (PAY CLOSE ATTENTION TO THIS)\n{MOST_RECENT_REACTION}\n\n## AVAILABLE OPTIONS\n{CHOICES_INFO}\n\n## CRITICAL REQUIREMENTS\n- DIRECT CONTINUATION: Choices MUST be direct responses to the EXACT situation described in the most recent narrative\n- ACKNOWLEDGE NPCs: If NPCs are speaking or acting in the narrative, choices MUST acknowledge their presence and actions\n- MAINTAIN CONTINUITY: DO NOT suggest actions that contradict what's already happening (e.g., don't suggest hiding if you're already in conversation)\n- REFERENCE SPECIFICS: Each choice should reference specific elements from the most recent narrative\n- TELEGRAPH RISKS: Choices that build pressure MUST include language that signals risk/danger/tension\n- SPECIFIC CONSEQUENCES: If a choice could cause health/focus/reputation loss, this MUST be implied in the description\n- PROPORTIONAL LANGUAGE: Higher pressure gains require stronger risk language\n\n## STRICT CONTINUITY EXAMPLES\nIf NPC says: \"Hand over your coins or I'll gut you!\"\n✓ GOOD: \"I reach for my coin purse - I slowly pull out my meager savings, though I worry this won't satisfy the bandit's greed.\"\n✗ BAD: \"I hide behind a cart - I duck behind a nearby cart to avoid being seen.\" (CONTINUITY BREAK - already being confronted!)\n\nIf narrative states: \"The guard watches me suspiciously from the gate...\"\n✓ GOOD: \"I approach confidently - I walk toward the guard with purpose, though his hand remains near his weapon.\"\n✗ BAD: \"I sneak past unseen - I slip into the shadows to avoid detection.\" (CONTINUITY BREAK - already being watched!)\n\nYour response MUST be valid JSON with NO text outside the JSON structure.\nEach choice MUST directly respond to the current narrative state exactly as described."
}
